HEADWORD: Disgavel
<hw>Dis*gav"el</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Disgaveled</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr> or
